jasima.core.experiment
Interface FullFactorialExperiment.ComplexFactorSetter

All Superinterfaces:
Serializable
Enclosing class:
FullFactorialExperiment
public static interface FullFactorialExperiment.ComplexFactorSetter
extends Serializable

Allows finer control of the way a base experiment is configured than the usual mechanism using JavaBean properties. If an object implementing ComplexFactorSetter is passed as a value when calling addFactor(String, Object) then instead of setting a bean property the method configureExperiment(Experiment) is called.

See Also:
FullFactorialExperiment.addFactor(String, Object)
